# Cloudflare Pages redirects — Tarumak Studio
# Regenerated during the July 2026 GSC indexing-recovery round.
# All rules are single-hop 301s — none of these chain into each other.

# ── 1. Domain canonicalization ──────────────────────────────────────
# https://tarumakstudio.com is canonical. www and http variants must
# 301 straight to it. NOTE: these rules only take effect once
# www.tarumakstudio.com is attached as a custom domain on this same
# Cloudflare Pages project — GSC currently shows both http:// and
# https://www variants returning 5xx, which means www isn't correctly
# connected yet at the DNS/Pages level. That's a dashboard action, not
# a file one — see the report for the exact steps. These rules will
# start working the moment that connection exists, with no further
# code change needed.
https://www.tarumakstudio.com/*  https://tarumakstudio.com/:splat  301
http://www.tarumakstudio.com/*   https://tarumakstudio.com/:splat  301
http://tarumakstudio.com/*       https://tarumakstudio.com/:splat  301

